info.keywords: PET tracer alignment,diffeomorphic imaging,image processing,multiplexed tracers
info.name: pumaz
info.summary: PUMA (PET Universal Multi-tracer Aligner) is a robust and efficient tool for aligning images from different PET tracers. It leverages advanced diffeomorphic imaging techniques to offer high-precision alignment for multiplexed tracer images. PUMA aims to significantly enhance the accuracy and reproducibility of PET image studies.
